Set up BerkeleyDB Instructions
------------------------------

1. Point the berkeleydb and berkeleydb_examples variables to db.jar and dbexamples.jar 
in the buildfiles\jars folder.

STOP HERE IF YOU JUST WANT TO BUILD THE PROJECT

2. Anything that uses the BerkeleyDB needs to have the dll's in the java.library.path VM variable

3. Add the following parameter to a new Run configuration for any BerkeleyDB test class:
	-Djava.library.path=<path to the berkeleydb_binary folder on your computer>